am wakken daɣen i d-yella ufraq n ddeqs n tɣawsiwin i yigerdan leḥlawat tičupiḍin
dahi i yezdeɣ yidir-nni i icennun a baba inuba
bɣiɣ lemmer ad sleɣ xersum tikelt i rray n lwennas qbel ad ad tt-gezmeɣ
tezdeɣ deg yiwet n taddart deg udrar
amek i nezmer ad neḥbes smawil waɛmaṛ u belḥaǧ
ad tekkat lehwa nezzeh seg zgelli
imiren inelmaden akken ma llan ǧǧan-t rewlen
mačči d ayla-nsen kan i sen-yerɣan yedda ula d ayla n wiyaḍ
ad t-ḥemdeɣ gar yiḥeqqiyen di tlemmast n unejmaɛ
akka si zik si zik akka si zzman n zik seg wasmi heddren iɣersiwen
twalaḍ wehmen ula d iɣersiwen deg wayen i la ttwalin
awal-nsen itezzi ɣef tsertit mačči ɣef tɣuri neɣ anadi ɣef tmusni
asmi i d-yettwaxleq lmal yettunefk-asen rray ad xtiren ttawil swayes ara qablen ddunit
anta ay d taselmadt ay tḥemmled akk
leǧnas meṛṛa ad ken-keṛhen ɣef ddemma n yisem-iw
a baba uwten-aɣ a mmi ɛeqlen-aɣ
yuba yesɣa-d tanfult ɣer sidi ɛli bunab
ɛeddan kra n wussan munir yuɣ-d akanic yerna-d abirmuda awezlan anect n tkiluḍt
ɣef waya ay ttamneɣ s tɣemsa
ɣas akken yedda d sima deg tkerrust
iwacu d-tuɣeḍ yiwet n tbanant kan
llan widen yugin ammus bɣan tezdeg s ṣṣabun n marseille
ur mennɛen ara si lbaṭel-nni i xedmen
maɣef ay tzerrew taninna yal ass
nenna-d basṭa leḥqaṛa di tmurt n leqbayel
n yiɣallen n usellek ad txeddem ass d yiḍ yal ass
talɣa-a d tin n yizimer abaṭuc
acuɣer i ttarwent tlawin deg tesɛa n wagguren
ur tezmir ara ad tili yid-s
ur ɣ-ttaǧǧan ara ad nekcem s urti
imugda ɣlin deg tazla ɣef imeḍqan d usuṛdi
d ccetla n uẓaɣaṛ rnant-d tmellalin
ad ilint tid ara yesɛun ulawen n wuzzal s wacu ara qablent anect-a n karuh
aḥbib n uḥbib iḥubb-it wul-iw ad as-fkeɣ ad yečč ad ǧǧeɣ iman-iw
d awezɣi fell-aneɣ ad nezger asif-a
nna ḍrifa teɣra cwiṭ ar yimṛabḍen n iṛumyen
ad cudden imeqqranen-nsen s leqyud n wuzzal
segmi teḍra tedyant n katia bengana
ttaḍsan ɣef yiman-nsen amek akken llan
uffan-d iman-nsen di taggara ḥeṣlen d acu ara xedmen
d acu ay tezmer taninna ad teg
umnen s rebbi maɛna nɣan ayen id-yexleq
tikkelt-a azemmur yurew ma d ilindi ulac maḍi
iyyat ad neddari da ɣef unẓar-a
yeffeɣ leɛtab n yuba ɣer tafat
wid ur nxeddem ur ttafen ara ččen
ad d-tesɛuḍ acqcic ad s-tsemmiḍ ismaɛil
ad d-nesmekti dakken amaynut yerza kan iqbayliyen i yettidiren di lɣerba
meẓẓyan yeɛreḍ ad idafeɛ ɣef yiman-is
d acu i yečča yuba d imensi
zgan ttwessin iman-nsen am wakken d agerruj i d-werten ɣef yimawlan-nsen
iwakken ad ten-ḥerzeɣ alamma d taggara
bɣiɣ ad rnuɣ ad ṭṭseɣ cwiṭ
argaz n uxxam tameṭṭut d agerruj
imɣaṛen nwan d nutni kan i yesɛan lḥeqq
